== ibikorwa Yakoze ==
Kabera ni we washinze kandi akaba na perezida w’ikigo cya Sinema cy’u Rwanda(Rwanda Cinema Center), umuryango ugamije guteza imbere inganda za firime mu gihugu. <ref name="ALL">Kisambira, Timothy. [http://allafrica.com/stories/200804071400.html Rwanda: The Golden Experience of the Silver Screen], [[AllAfrica.com]], April 6, 2008. Accessed February 26, 2009.</ref> <ref name="NEW">Gathoni, Peninnah. [http://www.newtimes.co.rw/index.php?issue=13816&article=13639 Fifth Film Festival to be held in June], ''[[The New Times (Rwanda)|The New Times]]'', 2009. Accessed February 26, 2009.</ref> Kabera yabanje gushyiraho Ikigo nk'umuryango uzahugura abakora amafilime mashya ariko, kuva 2005, iki kigo cyamenyekanye cyane mugutegura iserukiramuco rya cinema ngarukamwaka. <ref name="INDEP">Bloomfield, Steve. [https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/africa/welcome-to-hillywood-how-rwandas-film-industry-emerged-from-genocides-shadow-463541.html Welcome to Hillywood: how Rwanda's film industry emerged from genocide's shadow], ''[[The Independent]]'', August 30, 2007. Accessed February 26, 2009.</ref> <ref name="ALL" /> <ref name="NEW" /> Iserukiramuco rya sinema mu [[Rwanda]], ryiswe "Hillywood" kubera izina ry'u [[Rwanda]] ryiswe "Igihugu cy'imisozi igihumbi", ni umunsi mukuru w'ingendo. Bitewe n'icyifuzo cya Kabera cyo kwerekana amafilime ku bantu benshi bashoboka, iserukiramuco ntiribera mu murwa mukuru wa [[Kigali|Kigali gusa]] ahubwo ni filime, cyane cyane izakozwe n'abakora amafilime yo mu Rwanda, . <ref name="INDEP" /><ref>https://theculturetrip.com/africa/rwanda/articles/eric-kabera-keeper-of-rwanda-s-memory/</ref> Kabera yatangaje ko ibirori bizatera intambwe yo kutibanda gusa ku kibazo cya jenoside; kurusha ibindi bibazo byimibereho y'u [[Rwanda]] . <ref name="ABC">[http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2008/03/28/2201394.htm Don't mention the genocide: Rwanda film industry moves on], [[Australian Broadcasting Corporation]], March 28, 2008. Accessed February 26, 2009.</ref><r